{"tid":1870551,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"張建宗稱「謠言」跟病毒一樣　需全力抗擊","createTime":"2020-02-09T02:18:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-10T01:03:31.000Z","uid":83713,"like":2,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"40136e8b0f7b6b828575d148d2d61d8848b76cba","tid":1870551,"uid":83713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T02:18:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1507513-20200209.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1507513-20200209.htm&d=CEXeqV9R6719hdRRqmVjOogmK84TLJm0fByd7TIP4s4%3D&h=3f5cb343\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1507513-20200209.htm&h=6471abeb\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1507513-20200209.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n政務司司長張建宗表示，因應新型冠狀病毒感染疫情，特區政府以更嚴厲和果斷的措施應對，進一步壓縮香港和內地的跨境人流，新措施實施後首天，取得良好成效，從內地入境的人數大幅下跌。<br />\n<br />\n張建宗在網誌表示，近日有謠言指本港食米和日用品等物資短缺，他重申防控措施不影響內地與香港的貨運，因跨境貨車司機可獲豁免強制檢疫。政府已與主要食品供應商溝通，食品目前供應正常，沒有來貨不足問題，主要食品類別包括食米、麵食等有足夠存貨，市民毋須擔心。他又說抗疫期間，市民從多個渠道收到不同的資訊，留意到有的是惡意散播的謠言，唯恐天下不亂，危言聳聽，容易釀成公眾混亂和社會恐慌。他認為「謠言」跟病毒一樣，要全力抗擊，呼籲市民切勿輕信謠言，不要中圈套。　<br />\n<br />\n張建宗說，疫情的威脅是雪上加霜，進一步打擊經濟及整個社會，經營環境短期內難見好轉，部分行業業務低迷，未來可能出現結業潮，失業率會上升。<span style=\"color: red;\">特區政府會密切注視疫情對各行業的影響，提供適切協助</span>，政府亦正檢視早前因應社會事件推出的多輪紓緩措施，有需要時會延長有效期，甚或加大力度，呼籲商舖業主本着同舟共濟的精神，向租戶提供協助。<br />\n<br />\n他又說，多年來，香港建立了高效率的醫療系統，水平及質素享譽國際，全賴醫護人員的努力，在此困難時期，更必須同舟共濟，上下一心。張建宗強調政府重視每一位醫護人員，全力支援需要，包括盡力在全球採購防護物資，優先供醫護人員使用。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n協助？你買到口罩未呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af217278fd27045f540730d13c15291fdbcd6c51","tid":1870551,"uid":186,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T02:25:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">連登稱「謊言」跟病毒一樣 需全力抗擊<br />\n</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"39228dc2915a8933b54ff20e293e9dec2d76a99e","tid":1870551,"uid":54303,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"af217278fd27045f540730d13c15291fdbcd6c51","tid":1870551,"uid":186,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T02:25:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">連登稱「謊言」跟病毒一樣 需全力抗擊<br />\n</span></strong></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T02:28:01.000Z","msg":"支那官媒咪就係最大謠言製造者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d67c76469e423c11de3e16356792c49e189ac77e","tid":1870551,"uid":71748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T02:29:05.000Z","msg":"一有貨就掃曬仲謠言"},{"pid":"ad5f8930dc2e8fdc9fa0203830fd853fbca885a5","tid":1870551,"uid":172349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T02:30:18.000Z","msg":"謠言多因為政府無全力抗擊病毒呀嘛<br />\n<br />\n因果關係都未搞清，屌"},{"pid":"45318f8b3d18aa76b673ea3eda1839d0c07a7268","tid":1870551,"uid":105976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T03:08:58.000Z","msg":"謠言就係港共不完全封關有作用<br />\n謠言就係港共保障到公眾安全"},{"pid":"5393ca5fc6c42df8cea1468bb57a2b603580db69","tid":1870551,"uid":121197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T03:12:20.000Z","msg":"自己帶頭講大話嘅叫人唔好信謠言"},{"pid":"095d62e90d57efe6259b91fd66e96bb51f39bc87","tid":1870551,"uid":126366,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T03:13:28.000Z","msg":"張匪收皮啦 獨裁狗隻狗"},{"pid":"99d4ba424455c3b8967e440773138d5c42b7f6ff","tid":1870551,"uid":128117,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T03:14:21.000Z","msg":"03年夠係咩都話「謠言」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"657f799d70d0643deb9f70ce74d2e2d24650f64f","tid":1870551,"uid":37528,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T03:15:56.000Z","msg":"張建宗跟病毒一樣，需全力抗擊"},{"pid":"a8f33c705fa2e69c298c77e1d064ef67c8da8a01","tid":1870551,"uid":84172,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T03:19:41.000Z","msg":"咪就係因為你個政府咁垃撚圾<br />\n大家咪恐慌到乜都信囉<br />\n仲講<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6809cdae5b6e755081c05cd237846ab20fd4d5bc","tid":1870551,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T03:21:17.000Z","msg":"開頭唔知話無事咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85d7c5d630199de57500d6e650bf41a613a09828","tid":1870551,"uid":66202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T03:25:40.000Z","msg":"之前有人謠傳口罩會有大貨返咁點計<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35afa55d366430c88871d49687f4ce42833319f0","tid":1870551,"uid":161417,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T03:32:21.000Z","msg":"佢地宜家叫人唔好囤貨，證明咗佢地不知幾想維穩，我地應該調返轉頭全力囤貨至係 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2672fa94ec306071d4064ecac545d2217d728dcb","tid":1870551,"uid":30247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T03:34:39.000Z","msg":"他續稱，政府本月至今已促成800萬個口罩供港，作零售市場用途，並正與內地聯繫，促成2400萬個口罩供港，合共3200萬個將供應市場。<br />\n<br />\n去哂邊??? 洗唔洗搵黑警拉張建宗"},{"pid":"79516470b3c9e7362537c27b5dc13a22b1ffe2ff","tid":1870551,"uid":103981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T03:35:21.000Z","msg":"到左呢刻<br />\n你口中既謠言比你呢個所謂班子都更有市場<br />\n因為你地比起謠言更加不堪"},{"pid":"0f8efc6bc59bec89285b0fecfb4fbdb1837d919a","tid":1870551,"uid":44980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T03:37:35.000Z","msg":"可防可控"},{"pid":"eadc7ff78b818080b9c596f1ce4521f39749a25d","tid":1870551,"uid":185656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T03:43:43.000Z","msg":"警甴病毒殺傷力仲大過武肺病毒"},{"pid":"0ebad9446a33f2dd4e5f6a2664448fd411871d15","tid":1870551,"uid":31017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T03:49:58.000Z","msg":"不造謠，不傳謠，不信謠<b